{"tid":1896363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家 新選民登記截止日期係5月2號","createTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T14:33:19.000Z","uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2daa7babdb2764c2619d0dc6c78958a652640e1","tid":1896363,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"根據選舉事務處資料，2020年選民登記周期法定限期如下:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新登記申請：2020年5月2日<br />\n更改登記資料申請：2020年4月2日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=4c0d7532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n(留意:只要你喺2020年7月25日或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，選舉事務處於2月5日起至4月期間按相關選舉法例陸續向約九萬名選民發出查訊信件，要求他們確認或更新其登記住址。如果有收到信，係需要喺5月2日或之前回覆，否則會被納入在今年6月1日或之前發表的『取消登記名單』內。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/05/P2020020500513.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F05%2FP2020020500513.htm&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=6d2adcdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/05/P2020020500513.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n想知自己有冇被取消選民資格，自己click入選民資料網上查閱系統睇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=dd4041ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩之前仲未登記選民嗰班朋友，盡一盡公民責任，登記番先。<br />\n登記左選民嘅，自己睇下有冇收到信。<br />\n<br />\n睇完依個post麻煩推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f82edd5b25ee5f9001c7311b5333e3ce5ce14b9","tid":1896363,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"推，7月25前18,登記做選民"},{"pid":"6e8e5dd6db50264e39c76c5739440647785319e2","tid":1896363,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"界別分組同選舉委員會都係空左係咩意思？"}]}